DOC.TE:
   Already, the Chunky Soup curse is part of NFL folklore. The word
has been out for weeks: Make a Chunky Soup commercial, brace yourself
for the unseen evil that already has claimed the following:

   The roster includes Patrick Eaves, son of NHL alum Mike Eaves;
Eric Nystrom, son of former New York Islander standout Bobby Nystrom;
Zach Parise, son of long-time NHL forward J.P. Parise; and Ryan
Suter, son of 1980 U.S. Olympian Bob Suter and nephew of recently
retired defenseman Gary Suter. At 17, Ryan Suter is the youngest on
the team and is considered immensely promising.
